    <!-- Help & Support -->
    <string name="faq_title">Frequently Asked Questions</string>
    <string name="faq_1_question">How do I add new products?</string>
    <string name="faq_1_answer">Tap the floating primary (+) button on the home screen or go to the Products tab and click Add Item. Enter the name, selling price, and initial stock units.</string>
    <string name="faq_2_question">Does Storentry work without internet?</string>
    <string name="faq_2_answer">Yes, absolutely! Storentry operates 100% offline. All inventory records, alerts, and transaction history are stored securely inside your device database, making it lightning-fast and reliable even in zero-network areas.</string>
    <string name="faq_3_question">What are Low Stock alerts?</string>
    <string name="faq_3_answer">You can configure a custom low-stock threshold for each product. The moment your inventory drops below this number, the product status reflects \"Out of Stock\" or \"Low Stock\" with real-time reactive notifications.</string>
    <string name="faq_4_question">How do cloud backups and syncs work?</string>
    <string name="faq_4_answer">Free tier users can manually backup database updates by logging in and clicking \"Sync Now\" in Settings. Premium subscribers can toggle \"Auto-Sync\" to automatically upload and keep multiple devices synchronized in real-time.</string>
